                subtype="historical-document" type="document" xml:id="d266">
                <note rend="inline" type="source">852.48/1458: Telegram</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Secretary of State</gloss> to the
                        Minister in Portugal</hi> (<persName type="to">
                        <hi rend="italic">Fish</hi>
                    </persName>)</head>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1943-03-31T23:00:00-04:00"
                            >March 31, 1943—11 p.m.</date>
                    </dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>550. Your 34, March 27 to Murphy repeated to Department. The Department is taking
                    this matter up both in London and in Algiers. Are French refugees actually
                    arriving in Portugal now?</p>
                <p>Repeat to Madrid as Department’s 742.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Hull</hi>
                    </signed>
                </closer>
            </div>
        </body>
    </text>
